dct_description_sm: Reprinted 1928. United States Navy. Hydrographic Office. U.S. Navy Hydrographic Office. North Decimal Degree 78.000000. South Decimal Degree -69.000. East Decimal Degree 100.000. West Decimal Degree 60.0000. Map shows boundaries of South Pacific Mandate (Nan-Yo), and colonial insular possesion. Map no. 1262a. Small corrections printed Mar '28.
